{"tid":1720881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"作為一個司機  我真係好驚睇錯行車線","createTime":"2019-11-14T13:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T13:28:42.000Z","uid":31336,"like":77,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"9c47bfe70493b9fee33e3c95cd01ad82759e8a62","tid":1720881,"uid":31336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:30:15.000Z","msg":"港島啲線特別難睇   一唔覺意睇錯 亂就好易行錯<br />\n搞到塞到後面都夠衰  一陣撞埋仲死<br />\n<br />\n依家咁嘅時勢  遇到rb 都話有人落車清<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果地下啲線亂哂  一時睇到又睇唔到  <br />\n地下指示又錯哂  我真係會睇唔切嫁<br />\n撞左又睇線決定邊個啱    到時實有排嘈  唯有揸慢啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">啲線唔係一時三刻改得返</span><br />\n<br />\n紅隧收費亭前  都已經要cut黎cut去  一陣啲線亂哂我實停喺道唔敢行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf83ebd4c1d5f6c715dc328b7bad2e2d418b684","tid":1720881,"uid":190793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:30:52.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c06c0389e1902d9bd8a2533dc4103d0c20602351","tid":1720881,"uid":31336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:30:54.000Z","msg":"頂  開錯台添"},{"pid":"a027b17a7a9e0663ab08f78681fd87c9e07201db","tid":1720881,"uid":31336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:31:06.000Z","msg":"唔好推啊"},{"pid":"9fa0f443fa12c5f84ec5709d5b7db9eeb68fb5e2","tid":1720881,"uid":31336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:31:46.000Z","msg":"一陣埋大班人睇到點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb02384ed78dfc02e6873c7299dd112747263347","tid":1720881,"uid":20